<i>do space and time also vanish there?</i>

8
00:00:37.458 --> 00:00:40.458
<i>Or would space and time</i>

9
00:00:40.541 --> 00:00:44.291
<i>be tied together</i>
<i>and be part of an endless cycle?</i>

10
00:00:44.916 --> 00:00:48.333
