12
00:00:54.041 --> 00:00:55.458
<i>Tick-tock.</i>

13
00:00:55.958 --> 00:00:57.500
<i>Tick-tock.</i>

14
00:00:58.083 --> 00:00:59.333
<i>Tick-tock.</i>

15
