<i>to the Winden police.</i>

75
00:07:00.625 --> 00:07:03.750
<i>There have been repeated blackouts</i>
<i>in recent months</i>

76
00:07:04.625 --> 00:07:06.708
<i>Security and public facilities</i>

77
00:07:06.791 --> 00:07:09.250
<i>have not yet been...</i>

78
00:07:09.708 --> 00:07:12.375
<i>However.</i>
<i>power grid operators are promising</i>

79
00:07:12.458 --> 00:07:17.541
