130
00:11:56.750 --> 00:11:57.958
<i>the birds...</i>

131
00:12:00.500 --> 00:12:02.291
<i>Somehow it's all connected.</i>

132
00:12:02.375 --> 00:12:03.958
<i>I just don't know how.</i>

133
00:13:06.375 --> 00:13:09.625
<i>Where have you been?</i>
<i>The phones have been ringing all morning.</i>

134
00:13:09.708 --> 00:13:12.000
