139
00:13:21.958 --> 00:13:25.500
<i>He may have disappeared a long time ago.</i>
<i>Check the last 15 years. okay?</i>

140
00:13:26.041 --> 00:13:27.333
<i>Right. okay.</i>

141
00:13:27.416 --> 00:13:29.625
<i>-Anything else?</i>
<i>-No. Actually. there is.</i>

142
00:13:29.708 --> 00:13:31.083
<i>The red soil...</i>

143
00:13:31.166 --> 00:13:34.166
<i>We can't find any.</i>
<i>Not anywhere close to where he was found.</i>

144
00:13:34.250 --> 00:13:36.125
<i>It must've come from the crime scene.</i>

145
00:13:36.208 --> 00:13:38.125
<i>Get Jankowski to look into it.</i>

146
00:13:39.958 --> 00:13:42.083
<i>And what do we say about the dead boy?</i>

147
00:13:59.875 --> 00:14:01.000
<i>What time is it?</i>

148
00:14:01.791 --> 00:14:03.291
<i>Just past ten.</i>

149
00:14:09.958 --> 00:14:11.500
<i>Charlotte called.</i>

150
00:14:12.208 --> 00:14:15.375
<i>She still doesn't have</i>
<i>a search warrant for the power plant.</i>

151
00:14:17.541 --> 00:14:20.458
