166
00:17:05.708 --> 00:17:06.791
<i>Charlotte?</i>

167
00:17:07.708 --> 00:17:08.791
<i>Is everything okay?</i>

168
00:17:09.125 --> 00:17:13.375
<i>I missed your call</i>
<i>on the evening Mikkel disappeared.</i>

169
00:17:13.458 --> 00:17:15.375
