<i>to say I'd be home late.</i>

174
00:17:25.333 --> 00:17:26.833
<i>Nothing special.</i>

175
00:17:27.458 --> 00:17:29.875
<i>You were at the office</i>
<i>all day on Monday?</i>

176
00:17:30.500 --> 00:17:31.625
<i>Yes... Yeah.</i>

177
00:17:32.875 --> 00:17:34.541
<i>I was writing reports</i>

178
00:17:34.625 --> 00:17:37.291
